I13(i) beginning on the later of_

I14(I) January 1, 1990;

I14(II) the first day of the first calendar quarter that begins after the date on which the employer first began to pay compensation subject to this chapter; or

I14(III) July 1 of the third calendar year preceding that June 30; and

Q04

I13(ii) ending on that June 30.

