I12(1) the most favorable terms and conditions for assuring timely repayment and security as may then be reasonably available, and

I12(2) the requirement that any loan to the Corporation under this subsection be refinanced immediately out of the proceeds of the first sale by the issuance of debentures under section 726 of this title.

