I89. Supplementary unemployment insurance

I19(a) Eligible employees

I11Any employee of the Milwaukee Railroad_

I12(1) who (A) is employed by the restructured Milwaukee Railroad, and (B) is separated from that employment by reason of any reduction in service by such railroad prior to April 1, 1984; or

