I89. Statement of purpose

I11It is therefore declared to be the purpose of the Congress in this subtitle to provide for_

I12(1) the removal by a date certain of the Federal Government's obligation to subsidize the freight operations of Conrail;

I12(2) transfer of Conrail commuter service responsibilities to one or more entities whose principal purpose is the provision of commuter service; and

I12(3) an orderly return of Conrail freight service to the private sector.

